{"tid":2302964,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「重慶大廈感謝日」一年過去, 再次重臨究竟變成點呢?","createTime":"2020-11-27T13:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T12:49:21.000Z","uid":123926,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e79557b3d67d3984d56637815722a062ef4932","tid":2302964,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:55:13.000Z","msg":"利申,<br />\n我好少去尖沙嘴, 差唔多成年都無去過,<br />\n今次去到已經覺得條街好少人,<br />\n諗起一年前「重慶大廈感謝日」人山人海,<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1666545/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1666545/page/1</a><br />\n想八掛下究竟今時今日會變成咩情況?<br />\n<br />\n一去到大廈門口已經俾好多人不斷咁派咭片想拉你去佢地嘅餐廳度食,<br />\n講真真係有啲反感,<br />\n所以我走左,<br />\n但其中一個追到我去 ISQUARE,<br />\n見佢咁有誠意, 而且我又想食咖喱,<br />\n所以就跟左佢上去.<br />\n上到去就明點解佢地要咁駁命拉客,<br />\n由 7點幾坐到差不多9點都只係得我地呢一枱客,<br />\n仲要今日係星期五晚, 理應係最多人出街食飯嘅日子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食物水準唔錯, 幾好食,<br />\n雖然比想象中貴少少不過都算係合理價錢嘅,<br />\n總括黎講係可以多啲支持"},{"pid":"acce7574d57382f3360f7b037bdc0b3cb8e49a66","tid":2302964,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fe7247839c6883b6015071947fceb221a4ab92","tid":2302964,"uid":273545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:59:05.000Z","msg":"下次去拍拖有冇得撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c578d6206ec9d20efd4cc0265ee39a7f01c30a8e","tid":2302964,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:59:25.000Z","msg":"唉 唔去了"},{"pid":"a31b088f5367a4cc44893ca64e4ec09986f973ef","tid":2302964,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e0a13a9886316397bccb4b1afb6a5abf7e6195","tid":2302964,"uid":37525,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14